results.overview: German daily news program, the oldest still existing program on German television.
results.name: Tagesschau

results.overview: SRF Tagesschau is the title of a current affairs show on German-speaking Swiss public channel SRF 1. The main edition is broadcast at 19:30 and further editions are shown around noon and at the end of daily broadcasting. In 1990, another news show called 10vor10 was added.
results.name: SRF Tagesschau
